	(3,'School Life','/images/crazy_courses/2019/10/02/f2EhWaZz5d9403d03859a.jpg','School life is best!! For sure may be today u are small to realize but the school is the only place in your life where you spend your 15 years .\r\n\r\nThe school buildings , benches ,teachers have seen u growing .. they have seen you developing from a toddler to a teenager ,\r\n\r\nThey have seen the most important phase of your life . Those building will be the lifelong witness of your smile, of ur innocence , of ur laugh , of ur cries and most importantly of ur happiness and Joy as a child and as student.',1,1,1,'2018-09-25 16:42:08','2019-10-02 01:56:32',NULL),
	(4,'Transportation','/images/crazy_courses/2019/10/02/cmPIfJ2U5d940314da0b8.png','Transport or transportation is the movement of humans, animals and goods from one location to another. In other words, the action of transport is defined as a particular movement of an organism or thing from a point A to a Point B. Modes of transport include air, land (rail and road), water, cable, pipeline and space. The field can be divided into infrastructure, vehicles and operations. Transport enables trade between people, which is essential for the development of civilizations',1,1,1,'2018-09-25 16:43:23','2019-10-02 01:53:25',NULL),
