	(3226,'fell','v','fel','rơi',NULL,'<p>danh từ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>an amount of timber cut.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>đ&ocirc;̣ng từ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>cut down (a tree).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><q>Up on a ridge to the right of us, someone has been felling an oak tree all day.</q></p>\r\n\r\n<p>từ đồng nghĩa:&nbsp;cut down,&nbsp;chop down,&nbsp;hack down,&nbsp;saw down,&nbsp;clear</p>\r\n\r\n<p>t&iacute;nh từ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>of terrible evil or ferocity; deadly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><q>sorcerers use spells to achieve their fell ends</q></p>\r\n\r\n<p>từ đồng nghĩa:&nbsp;murderous,&nbsp;savage,&nbsp;violent,&nbsp;vicious,&nbsp;fierce,&nbsp;ferocious,&nbsp;barbarous,&nbsp;barbaric,&nbsp;monstrous,&nbsp;cruel,&nbsp;ruthless,&nbsp;sanguinary</p>\r\n\r\n<p>đ&ocirc;̣ng từ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>move downward, typically rapidly and freely without control, from a higher to a lower level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><q>bombs could be seen falling from the planes</q></p>\r\n\r\n<p>từ đồng nghĩa:&nbsp;drop,&nbsp;descend,&nbsp;come down,&nbsp;go down,&nbsp;plummet,&nbsp;plunge,&nbsp;sink,&nbsp;dive,&nbsp;tumble,&nbsp;cascade</p>',1,'2018-06-19 08:03:38','2018-06-19 08:03:38'),
	(3227,'calendar','n','ˈkaləndər','Lịch',NULL,'<p>danh từ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>a chart or series of pages showing the days, weeks, and months of a particular year, or giving particular seasonal information.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><q>For the weather obsessed, the calendar features information on the average temperatures each month, the average rainfall and the cycles of the moon throughout the year.</q></p>\r\n\r\n<p>đ&ocirc;̣ng từ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>enter (something) in a calendar or timetable.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><q>Indeed, the recently calendared Scottish records indicate that Anna was &lsquo;engaged in startling vigorous political activity&rsquo; from 1590 to 1603.</q></p>',1,'2018-06-20 10:49:44','2018-06-20 10:49:44'),
